<title>USA: Imperial Bancorp Q4 net rises.</title>
<headline>Imperial Bancorp Q4 net rises.</headline>
<dateline>LOS ANGELES 1997-01-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Financial Summary</p>
<p>		 (Dollars in thousands, except per-share data)</p>
<p>		    Three months ended	     Year ended</p>
<p>			   Dec. 31,		     Dec. 31,</p>
<p>			 1996	   1995	  1996	  1995</p>
